column3: I am a soldier in the service of Lord Aurvael de Haillenarte. If you seek my master, I am afraid he is occupied with preparations for a new undertaking.
I am a soldier in the service of Lord Aurvael de Haillenarte. If you seek my master, he is presently in the Firmament for a new undertaking.
However, I should be pleased to assist you with any lockboxes you may possess, as well as trade with you for your sky pirate spoils.
Owing to recent developments, these items are not as common as they once were, but should you chance to acquire them, please feel free to come to me.
If you seek my lord Aurvael, I am afraid he is occupied with preparations for a new undertaking.
